		Transitioning Into Retirement
	
	













 
			
			
				Transitioning Into Retirement
			 
		






Transitioning from the working world into retirement may be smoother if you take the right steps.








 Learn the 7 steps of Transitioning into Retirement









	
	
		The Importance of Planning
	
	













 
			
			
				The Importance of Planning
			 
		






When should you begin to take Social Security? How much should you budget for retirement? What if you have unforeseen medical costs or other expenses? These are questions every person approaching retirement should consider. Developing a plan for retirement in advance will help you determine the actions you need to take to prepare for a ﬁnancially secure future.








 Learn about planning for your retirement 


















 

